citation.case_name: In Re Discipline of Ayeni. No. D-2374

html:
541 U.S. 933

IN RE DISCIPLINE OF AYENI.
No. D-2374.

Supreme Court of United States.

March 22, 2004.

1

Shola Rannie Ayeni, of Stafford, Va., is suspended from the practice of law in this Court, and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
